Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.68,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of White...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...had a very beautiful, good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.35,Main,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, the Girl of Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...had a very unsightly, evil heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:32.20,Main,,0,0,0,,...envied and hated the ever happy\Nand smiling Girl of White...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,...and thought of erasing her very existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.71,Main,,0,0,0,,...were listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:51.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...the two girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...were originally from one girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Now go...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.60,Main,,0,0,0,,...to their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:52.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:54.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:58.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:03.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:12.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.98,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, nice work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona, Akira, you both did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to the dressing room later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:20.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No. There are people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That's... for when we're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,--I'll be waiting.\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Just you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san {\i0}is... the Girl of Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,What's... happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, what happened to Futase-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,That's about all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.53,Main,,0,0,0,,This is confusing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,If Iona is this "Girl of Black"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.57,Main,,0,0,0,,...what does it have to do\Nwith Selector battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,And, about the Girl of White...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,White...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh, what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s conversation\Nonly lasted a short moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Urr...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,--Chiyori-{\i1}chan{\i0}?\N--If you have to use the toilet, just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Urrroooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,--Wha-?!\N--Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The excitement is over the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, she has spasms like this time-to-time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,so don't let it bother you folks,\Nand continue your talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:34.77,Main,,0,0,0,,So, the WIXOSS novel was\Nborn from the oath between
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:38.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Futase-{\i1}sensei {\i0}and Fumio-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Npassionate friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,It was first an Internet novel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:44.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,"Work Writing Stories"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:48.37,Main,,0,0,0,,After searching for ways\Nto become a novelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,...I found out that such an\Napproach was now possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:57.09,Main,,0,0,0,,"Thread to talk about Futase Fumio."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"Do you know Futase Fumio?"\N"Heard the writing's good."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.43,Main,,0,0,0,,"Web Novel Ranking"\N"Author: Futase Fumio"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect it to turn out this well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.02,Main,,0,0,0,,All of Chiyori is wailing\Nover your happy ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a dummy!\NWhat's so "happy" about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Fumio-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nwho became an LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Apparently, no one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Futase-{\i1}san {\i0}returning from\Nbeing an LRIG to human,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,only to be participating\Nin battles as a Selector is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the wish to become\Na novelist realized already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:41.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange to become a\NSelector again for that wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That is a strange thing for you to say as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You being an LRIG must mean\Nyou were once a Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You had a wish you wanted to realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:55.31,Main,,0,0,0,,...and thus you believed the\Nsweet words of your LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,...winning to become an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}wasn't willfully\Ntrying to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,She always worried for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure... even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your wish something that would satisfy\Nyou if it came true only for a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:21.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't your wish something that made sense\Nonly when it went beyond the moment, forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It... was a wish I wanted to last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Fumio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Her wish is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,To become a novelist meant that\Nshe wanted to live as a novelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Writing only two volumes doesn't give me\Nthe right to call myself a novelist yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm merely an ephemeral hollow of an existence\Nthat would fade once the writing stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish... truly begins when one\Nbelieves that it was fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't be realized until\Nit is fulfilled until death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:04.13,Main,,0,0,0,,There's... no end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:08.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Unlike Fumio, I haven't read many books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The only reason I could\Nsomehow write the novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:17.23,Main,,0,0,0,,...was because, as a Selector,\NI had first-hand knowledge of LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But soon the well of knowledge dries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's why she's having writer's block.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But, but, the power of friendship from the\Npassionate oath will save Futase-{\i1}sensei {\i0}from--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Reality isn't like stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Friendship and oaths don't help at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But, Sensei can...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't write even if I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, I can't stop writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:50.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Is what binds me,\Na mission or my promise to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't even tell now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:55.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...after living my life as Futase Fumio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:00.86,Main,,0,0,0,,By the looks of it, rather than\Nbeing an Eternal Girl's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.52,Main,,0,0,0,,...it's more fitting to call it a curse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,A curse where you're\Ncrushed by another's wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,and you live as another, only to\Nlose sight of who you once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to the white window room again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,If I don't meet her,\Nthe story can't continue...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, are you my next opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Or is it you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Which one of you will battle me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:32.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori-{\i1}chan {\i0}and I won't battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... So I guess that's it then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I can write a new chapter because of you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to write... I need to write...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You may be asserting something right,\Njust like a heroine from a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--That's not what I--\N--But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...some need to rely on Selector battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like Futase...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.84,Main,,0,0,0,,White room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Large window...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.42,Main,,0,0,0,,To Mayu-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.59,Main,,0,0,0,,White room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:14.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It must've been shocking, especially\Nwith how Chiyori admired the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Honestly, it was a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:42.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Especially when I think of how Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nmay be suffering because of my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if LRIGs become human again,\Nthis is too painful to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why we need to stop Selector battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I... thought that if all the battles went away,\Nno one would need to experience sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,...there are others who need it,\Neven when they know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:06.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Her situation is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,When I saw Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}before, she was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...that battling would\Nhelp her be her best again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:17.53,Main,,0,0,0,,We were able to meet because...\Nwe were Selectors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! You too, Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,...still want to release all\Nthe girls who became LRIGs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone to suffer\Nafter becoming an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,If there's a way to return Futase-{\i1}san {\i0}back to her\Nnormal self, then I want to look for that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Earlier, Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:53.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to save everyone, don't let needless\Nthings sway you, and show your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,...reminded me of what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:11:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}, thank you for your help in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}? What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Such a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It is Urith's request after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I actually had another favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What? I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's something I can only ask from you, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,But, she's probably going to say\Nshe doesn't want to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:56.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What is her most precious thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:59.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You take it from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to an interesting show...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home, grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Girl of Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Girl of Dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You envy everyone,\Nand bring sorrow to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:49.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You're hated by everyone,\Nand you hate everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a bad girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,A girl who's all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.65,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, hate, hate, hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You hate everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of Black brings misery to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,No... No, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Battling for eternity to bring misery to all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Such is the fate of the Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do...?\NDid she catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.97,Main,,0,0,0,,--How about medicine?\N--Let me go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold it! How are you going to make her take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't caught a cold or anything\Nsince becoming an LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you tell if you're cold\Nor have a fever? Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:44.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Does your stomach hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Why... is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.70,Main,,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can do, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...so concerned like that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.04,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.13,Main,,0,0,0,,...that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:01.30,Main,,0,0,0,,...I feel a little... cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You're of black, and you hate white things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Longing for white...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,...and wishing to be next to white...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...will just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...make the pain worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's calmed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,...about Iona being the "Girl of Black"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}... must know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's press for answers\Nwhen she's back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,If we became friends...\Nwould Iona-{\i1}san {\i0}open up to us more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,She's keeping secrets because of reasons\Nshe doesn't want to tell us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:58.19,Main,,0,0,0,,...had things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't say to Tama, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:07.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I only thought of my own feelings,\Nand didn't think about how Tama felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I hurt her with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,This time I want to do things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to start over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a softie, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:22.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You're making me sound bad for talking\Nabout pressing answers from her. Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's all start over, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,In a way where no one\Nneeds to sacrifice themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:43.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Hitoe-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s\Nfamily is getting worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:47.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I... stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup. Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:16:00.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I could stay too,\Nbut mom would get worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Both of you, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:07.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You have Iona-{\i1}san {\i0}to care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:10.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll call you when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:27.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I better hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,That took too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I was getting tired of all this waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:42.42,Main,,0,0,0,,We haven't done it since\Nwe got new LRIGs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you scared of losing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,...just hurt you even more than before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:17:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,If Hitoe isn't gonna battle me,\NI guess I'll go to Ru-ru's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:03.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get involved with Ruko anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The heck is with you ordering me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:12.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone trying\Nto hurt Ruko get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You piss me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:15.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You seriously piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:19.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't push your luck, you lame nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I decided... to start over with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, battle me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Show me how you're not gonna let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like she doesn't have her LRIG-lun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:36.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't sense one around-lun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.56,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like you can only\Nplay a normal game of WIXOSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:53.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This is going to mess with Urith's request...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,She's going to be let down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,No... I can't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith is going to hate me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Dump me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,She's going to dump me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.38,Main,,0,0,0,,No... No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I'm sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You take it from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to an interesting show...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you're around...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...everything's gonna be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Rain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,The rain's gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope Hitoe isn't getting drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?\NYou were in pain all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It... wasn't a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you did say you were cold, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:07.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Doing this is of no use to an LRIG like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:13.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, grandma, I'll get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, did the rain get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe wouldn't cooperate, so she's all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"Create" "Urith" "I got her"\NCorrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my Ru-ru! So Aki-lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell you where you need to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:40.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup... Yup, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.39,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hitoe?!\N--Shut up, ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:47.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I got it! I'll go, so please stop hurting Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring Iona with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Selectors and LRIGs have to be\Nbuddy-buddy and be together, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait... Iona isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You're coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.54,Main,,0,0,0,,How's Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}has Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,She said to come now with Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:17.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine. Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not letting this go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:26.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:27.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:57.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Totally horrible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this bite mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Now what am I going to do at the next shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one who started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for not being\Nnext to her as her freaking LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:11.06,Main,,0,0,0,,And, where's Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Handling things like usual, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:19.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish you could've seen Hitoe\Ngetting all desperate and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, she was saying she was\Ngoing to protect Ru-ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Acting all cocky to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:24.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, once a nobody, always a nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to battle me\Nthat much, I'll battle you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:36.67,Main,,0,0,0,,But in return, I never want you\Nto do anything like this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oops! Looks like you're missing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,She came!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not part of the fun, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Existence is Dark Black"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A city of mazes with no exit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the sound of bells ringing{\i0}
